<h1>Mac and Java 7</h1>

<p>2013-10-09 16:54 Wednesday</p>

<p>想来想去，还是需要在 Mac 上安装 Java 7。Chrome 不能跑 Java 7 就让它不能跑吧，反正用的也不多。网上银行要用？实在不行就再改回来</p>

<h2>在 Mac 上安装 Java 7</h2>

<p>要在 Mac 上安装 Java，请按照以下步骤操作：</p>

<p>http://www.java.com/zh_CN/download/help/mac_install.xml</p>

<ol>
	<li>下载&nbsp;jre-7u6-macosx-x64.dmg&nbsp;文件。<br />
	在下载文件前，需查看并同意许可证协议的条款。</li>
	<li>双击 .dmg 文件以启动它</li>
	<li>双击程序包图标以启动安装向导</li>
	<li>安装向导将显示 &quot;Welcome to Java 7&quot;（欢迎使用 Java 7）安装屏幕。单击&nbsp;Continue（继续）</li>
	<li>在 &quot;Standard Install on Macintosh HD&quot;（Macintosh HD 上的标准安装）上，单击&nbsp;Install（安装）按钮</li>
	<li>安装完成后，将显示确认屏幕。单击&nbsp;Close（关闭）完成安装过程。</li>
</ol>

<table border="1" cellspacing="1">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>&nbsp;Mac OS X x64</td>
			<td>183.35 MB&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
			<td><a href="http://download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/7u40-b43/jdk-7u40-macosx-x64.dmg">&nbsp;jdk-7u40-macosx-x64.dmg</a></td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p>安装前</p>

<pre>
$ java -version
java version &quot;1.6.0_51&quot;
Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 1.6.0_51-b11-457-11M4509)
Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (build 20.51-b01-457, mixed mode)</pre>

<pre>
$ which java
/usr/bin/java</pre>

<pre>
$ ll /usr/bin/java
lrwxr-xr-x  1 root  wheel  74  8 11 14:19 /usr/bin/java -&gt; /System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/Current/Commands/java</pre>

<p>安装后</p>

<pre>
$ java -version
java version &quot;1.7.0_40&quot;
Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 1.7.0_40-b43)
Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (build 24.0-b56, mixed mode)</pre>

<pre>
$ which java
/usr/bin/java</pre>

<pre>
$ ll /usr/bin/java
lrwxr-xr-x &nbsp;1 root &nbsp;wheel &nbsp;74 &nbsp;8 11 14:19 /usr/bin/java -&gt; /System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Versions/Current/Commands/java
</pre>

